nodes.text: Doctor Saychel was a Human male who served as an officer within the New Republic Intelligence Service. He once worked with a Coruscant safe house located in the Government District alongside Showolter, and was in contact with Han Solo, Luke Skywalker, and Lando Calrissian. In 25 ABY he was sent to Nim Drovis to help in the interrogation of the Yuuzhan Vong priestess Elan and her familiar, Vergere.
